## Repository Purpose

This is the TaaS Plugin Ecosystem — a collection of TypeScript data source adapters that extend
the TaaS Gateway's Unified Capability Model (UCM). Each plugin wraps one external data provider API.

## The ONLY Valid Base Class

Every plugin MUST extend `SovereignAdapter` from `@taas/discovery`. Direct implementation of
`DataSource` from `@taas/interfaces` is forbidden.

```typescript
import { SovereignAdapter, AdapterConfig, DataCategory } from '@taas/discovery';

export class MyDataSource extends SovereignAdapter<MyResponseType, MyParamsType> {
  constructor(config: Partial<AdapterConfig> = {}) {
    super({
      name: 'Human Readable Name',      // required
      category: DataCategory.CUSTOM,    // required — must be a valid DataCategory value
      responseSchema: MyZodSchema,      // recommended — Zod schema for runtime validation
      capabilities: {
        supportsHistorical: false,       // required
        supportsRealtime: true,          // required
        methods: ['methodName'],         // required — at least one entry
      },
      ...config,
    });
  }

  protected async fetchData(params: MyParamsType, signal?: AbortSignal): Promise<MyResponseType> {
    // Use this.client (Axios instance). ALWAYS forward signal.
    const response = await this.client.get('https://api.example.com/v1/data', {
      params: { symbol: params.symbol },
      signal,  // <-- NEVER omit this
    });
    return response.data;
  }

  protected async getMockData(params: MyParamsType): Promise<MyResponseType> {
    // ZERO network calls here. Return hardcoded plausible data.
    return { value: 1234.56, timestamp: params.timestamp ?? Date.now() };
  }
}
```

## SovereignAdapter — Available Properties

| Property | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `this.id` | `string` | Auto-derived from `name`; or pass `id` in config |
| `this.name` | `string` | Human-readable name |
| `this.category` | `DataCategory` | Set in constructor |
| `this.capabilities` | `SourceCapabilities` | Set in constructor |
| `this.client` | `AxiosInstance` | Pre-configured HTTP client with SSRF protection |
| `this.apiKey` | `string \| undefined` | Set from `config.apiKey` |
| `this.useMocks` | `boolean` | True in test mode |
| `this.secretProvider` | `SecretProvider \| undefined` | For runtime secret retrieval |

